WEBVTT

00:00:05.109 --> 00:00:07.111 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
The city of Naples was chosen

00:00:07.111 --> 00:00:08.571 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
as the host city

00:00:08.571 --> 00:00:10.781 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
for the 30th edition of a sports event

00:00:10.781 --> 00:00:12.992 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
known as the Universiade.

00:00:14.285 --> 00:00:18.998 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The event took place from July 3 to 14, 2019,

00:00:18.998 --> 00:00:23.127 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and the participants were university athletes
from all over the world.

00:00:23.127 --> 00:00:27.006 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Public witnessing carts were organized
in areas of the city

00:00:27.006 --> 00:00:29.717 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
where the majority of visitors and athletes
would visit.

00:00:29.717 --> 00:00:33.262 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
One thousand two hundred and twenty-five
brothers and sisters in all

00:00:33.262 --> 00:00:35.639 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
took part in this initiative.

00:00:35.639 --> 00:00:38.058 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The enthusiasm of our brothers and sisters,

00:00:38.058 --> 00:00:40.019 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
along with Jehovah’s blessing,

00:00:40.019 --> 00:00:42.104 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
yielded excellent results.

00:00:42.104 --> 00:00:45.524 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
About 15 Chinese athletes approached us

00:00:45.524 --> 00:00:46.859 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
as soon as they recognized

00:00:46.859 --> 00:00:48.110 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
the logo of our website.

00:00:48.110 --> 00:00:50.613 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
One of them even said, “Ah, this is Jehovah!”

00:00:50.613 --> 00:00:52.615 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And that allowed for a nice conversation.

00:00:52.615 --> 00:00:56.493 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The brothers spent
a total of 6,000 hours witnessing,

00:00:56.493 --> 00:01:00.664 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
had 1,640 Bible-based conversations,

00:01:00.664 --> 00:01:04.209 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and placed 1,456 publications.

00:01:05.461 --> 00:01:07.463 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The brothers in Naples continue

00:01:07.463 --> 00:01:10.591 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“without letup
teaching and declaring the good news”

00:01:10.591 --> 00:01:12.635 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
at every opportunity.

